title.narrative: AR Provincial Maternal-Child Health Investment APL 2

description.narrative: The project development objectives are: (a) to increase access by eligible uninsured mothers and children to basic health services; (b) to strengthen the incentive framework for efficiency and focus on results between the national level and the Eligible Provinces and among Eligible Provinces and service providers by linking financing to both services actually rendered to the target populationand to the achievement of the MCHIP results as reflected by the selected ten tracers of the Trazadoras Matrix.
